# Learninx environment configuration.
#
# The app no longer uses a database. Lessons and quiz questions are defined in
# code (`src/lib/lessons.ts`) and per-visitor progress lives in a signed
# cookie (`src/lib/progress.ts`).
#
# Optional: a stable secret for signing the progress cookie. If unset, the
# server synthesises a per-process key. Set this in production so progress
# cookies survive deploys and restarts.

# LEARNINX_SECRET="replace-me-with-a-long-random-string"
